      "widgets_values": [
        "QUICK PANEL \u00b7 Z-IMAGE TURBO\n\n**Models:** #1 diffusion_models/`z_image_turbo_bf16.safetensors` \u00b7 #23 text_encoders/`qwen_3_4b.safetensors` (CLIPLoader type **qwen_image**) \u00b7 #24 `ae.safetensors`.\n\n**Smooth / anti-flicker:** **fixed** seed (#2); **Euler** + **turbo** scheduler; **CFG 1.0 flat** (#3); **8 steps flat** (#14) \u2014 distilled model degrades beyond ~8 steps; eased **strength** ramp #3 for calmer chaining; softened **motion** (#5 zoom); softened **noise** ramp; toned **sharp** (#22); weaker **negative** (#7); **704\u20131024-ish** natives work \u2014 here **960\u00d7544** for 16-aligned pixels.\n\n**Performance:** FP8 loaders on Ada/Hopper: UNET `#1` \u2192 `fp8_e4m3fn_fast` if supported.\n\n**Continuation:** Same as preset \u2014 init #8 \u00b7 #15 \u00b7 #19 / #20."
